THIRD-PARTY MATERIAL CAVEAT
---------------------------
The source Guide names, cites, and in places embeds third-party material that is
NOT public domain — including the EIA-748 EVM standard, MIL-STD-881D, the ICEAA
Cost Estimating Body of Knowledge, AACEI and PMI standards, and example tables
attributed to ©MCR, LLC and ©ICEAA. This pack references and paraphrases such
material in original words only and reproduces none of it verbatim; no third-party
licence is conveyed by, or required for, this pack. Anyone needing the underlying
standards must obtain them from their respective publishers.

